Afro-pop singer and songwriter, Lungisa Xhamela is expanding and taking his career to new heights and audiences. Already a budding star in the music business, the former Idols SA contestant is dipping his toe into the fashion pool. Lungisa has collaborated with Mazerata to feature in their new men’s shoe campaign, titled the Sound of Style.  The brand felt that Lungisa’s personal style made him the perfect fit for the campaign, which is allowing him to show off his style and sophistication like never before.   